  m_text: '

    Your goal is simple:

    Stay alive.

    

    Enemies attack
    in waves. Some waves may be deadly, others may bring rewards.

    

    Fight
    as long as you can, survive the chaos, and beat your best score!

    

    Basic
    Ship Controls:

    W / S / A / D - Move

    Left Shift - Move Up

    Left
    Ctrl - Move Down'
